&lt;li&gt;建立About頁面&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;建立Projects頁面&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;調整字體和行距&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;</description></item><item><title>關於</title><link>https://blog.beagleworks.net/tw/about/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://blog.beagleworks.net/tw/about/</guid><description>about</description></item><item><title>隱私權政策</title><link>https://blog.beagleworks.net/tw/privacy-policy/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://blog.beagleworks.net/tw/privacy-policy/</guid><description>privacy-policy</description></item></channel></rss>